Package org.sopra.api.command

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AdjustConsumerCommand
    A command to adjust the amount of energy used by a controllable consumer.
    AdjustmentCommand
    Extends the command interface with some information that is required to adjust either the production or consumption of energy if the corresponding energy node is controllable.
    AdjustProducerCommand
    A command to adjust the amount of energy generated by a controllable producer.
    BuildPowerPlantCommand
    A command that builds a power plant at a given transformer station.
    Command
    Commands are used to change the state of a scenario.
    CommandFactory
    The command factory creates new commands.
    UpgradeLineCommand
    A command that upgrades power lines.
